flowchart TD
  UI[Angular UI] --> GW[Gateway Service]
  GW --> K8S[Kubernetes Platform Service]
  GW --> DOCKER[Docker Runtime Service]
  GW --> SEC[Security Service]
  K8S --> KUBECTL[/kubectl mounted in /opt/nebula-tools/]
  DOCKER --> DOCKERCLI[/docker CLI + /var/run/docker.sock/]
  SEC --> TRIVY[/trivy if installed on host/]
  GW --> JAVA[/Java absolute path: /opt/java/openjdk/bin/java/]
  KUBECTL --> CLUSTER[(Kubernetes API)]
  DOCKERCLI --> ENGINE[(Docker Engine API)]
